		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />I had one of the redesigned ones and the audio was distorted (overmodulated). It was easily noticeable in the ring collect sound in Sonic. I think this was an inherent flaw in that model, and had to get one of the originals to get clean audio. At the very least, be sure you can check the audio first.

		

